pr_body:
# Proposed Changes
Basic Settings and functionality of the app.

* ### Basic App Settings and Settings handler.
 * Settings Handler called every time any settings changes.
 * Settings Handler called when app starts or restarts. 
* ### Getting the final list of blocked words. 
 * Fetching words from URL.
 * Getting user defined blocked words.
 * Removing user defined allowed words from the list of blocked words.
 * Getting list of Blocked words whenever app starts or restarts.
* ### Basic Message Filtering.
 * Message Filtering on editing/updating message.
 * Attachment description filtering.
 * Storing the stats for offending users.
* ### Displaying stats and slash command functionalities.
 * Displaying stats to admins and owners and error notify message to other users.
 * Opening a modal displaying stats through slash command.
 * Providing functionalities like clear records for offending users and banning users through the stats modal.
 * Clear records, ban and un-ban users through slash sub commands.
